The paper proposes a novel illegal vehicle parking detection system based on deep learning, specifically using the Single Shot MultiBox Detector (SSD) algorithm. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses optimizing the SSD algorithm, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of camera footage and tracking could also suggest the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the focus on real-time detection and robustness could indicate the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category.
